  "title": "Permanent Physiotherapist (Nursing Home, Jurong East + Yishun)",
  "description": "<p>We are actively hiring for a client in a Nursing Home setting in Singapore and we wish to invite interested therapist to apply the role.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Code:</strong> <strong>SNHW/29/01/PT</strong></p><p><strong>Permanent Senior Physiotherapist</strong></p><ul><li>Assess patients' physical conditions and develop tailored treatment plans.</li><li>Use manual therapy, therapeutic exercises, and specialized equipment to aid recovery.</li><li>Educate patients on injury prevention, posture correction, and lifestyle modifications.</li><li>Collaborate with doctors, occupational therapists, and other healthcare professionals.</li><li>Monitor patient progress and adjust treatments as needed.</li><li>Maintain accurate records of patient assessments and treatment plans.</li><li>Stay updated with the latest physiotherapy techniques and best practices.</li></ul><p><strong>Project Schedule</strong></p><ul><li>FY2026</li><li>5 full days per week (8 am - 5.30pm)</li><li>The Physiotherapist is expected to provide support at each facility on alternate days (Jurong East & Yishun)</li><li>Bachelor or Masters in Physiotherapy</li><li>Must be a Fully Registered AHPC ( Singapore )</li></ul><p><strong>Drop in your CV to: hr@pacificrehab.com.sg</strong></p><p><strong>Or WhatsApp 8022 6814</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Quick SIGN UP here : https://form.jotform.com/250558451726461</strong></p>",
